dirk jungé cfa  pitcairn home  client login     navigation menu home » dirk jungé cfa dirk jungé cfa chairman dirk jungé cfa is chairman of pitcairn company he also until recently served as chief executive officer of pitcairn a recognized global leader in the specialized family office marketplace he has been an innovator and leader in the family office for over  years a fourth generation member of the pitcairn family he was instrumental in establishing the firm as a multifamily office in  and led pitcairn’s pioneering transition to a  open architecture investment platform dirk is a consultant author and frequent speaker at conferences and seminars on issues related to the financial services industry family office family governance and succession planning dirk received the lifetime achievement award at the  family wealth report awards for his leadership and dedication to the family office industry in  family office exchange honored him with the fox founders award recognizing him as a pioneer in the wealth management industry in  he received the family office review for industry leadership award in recognition of his significant contributions to the family office industry and was also named for multifamily office ceo of the year his article “from family business conflict to family connectedness” appeared in the autumn  issue of family business magazine in addition in  he contributed a chapter for the handbook of family business and family business consultation a global perspective which explores the role of the multifamily office in a changing global economy widely recognized for his involvement in social and community affairs dirk sits on a variety of philanthropic and corporate boards including paramount resources ltd freeman company lb foster and the pennypack ecological restoration trust he is also a founding trustee and board member of the national philanthropic trust dirk is a member of the collaboration for family flourishing he is also a fellow of the family firm institute ffi and a recipient of the ffi barbara hollander award recognizing his commitment and dedication to education and learning in the field of family business he has completed ffi’s advanced certificate in family business advising he is a past member of the  society of the national constitution center and a past member of the james madison council of the library of congress he previously served on the boards of abington memorial hospital academy of the new church and ffi in march  he received pathnorth’s john c whitehead award given to individuals whose lives integrate meaning and contribution in  dirk was named a regional finalist in the ernst  young entrepreneur of the year program dirk received a bs in economics and finance from lehigh university and holds the designation of chartered financial analyst recent news family office reaps real dividends from wigmore association drain the swamp or a drain on the swamp pitcairn investment commentary “remain focused on the known” upcoming events human capital in the family enterprise – private event the value of collaboration lessons from the wigmore association – private event fox regional member briefing – invitation only contact info we have offices in philadelphia new york washington dc  upcoming events family office reaps real dividends from wigmore association drain the swamp or a drain on the swamp human capital in the family enterprise – private event the value of collaboration lessons from the wigmore association – private event pitcairn investment commentary “remain focused on the known” sitemaphome who we are what we do resources news and events contact us         offices in philadelphia new york  washington dc terms of use and privacy policy        pitcairn top dirk junge  ceo founder businessman  profile directorpedianet  list of ceos founders board members and company directors dirk junge check out list of companies and businesses related to dirk junge find out dirk junge address and contact detai